80
00:06:33,639 --> 00:06:43,022
[SPEAKER_04]: I also just wanted to say that we're going to discuss, we're going to bring this to the full committee in December, and we'll have a bigger discussion, and the Collins Center will be there.

81
00:06:43,102 --> 00:06:49,904
[SPEAKER_04]: But I briefly talked to the Collins Center, and, you know, they felt like 21 days was too short.

82
