[SPEAKER_04]: Because, I mean, it is true, the city council, a lot of city councils, including Medford's now, only meet every other week.

83
00:07:06,262 --> 00:07:09,925
[SPEAKER_04]: And 45 days is more standard.

84
00:07:11,286 --> 00:07:14,588
[SPEAKER_04]: I thought I was thinking maybe we could put 30 as a compromise.

85
