[SPEAKER_01]: Appointments take effect after 30 days unless City Council acts to approve it sooner.

140
00:10:53,719 --> 00:10:55,299
[SPEAKER_04]: Okay.

141
00:10:56,359 --> 00:10:58,160
[SPEAKER_01]: Or votes to veto.

142
