[SPEAKER_04]: That sounds good.

145
00:11:02,001 --> 00:11:05,882
[SPEAKER_01]: Does the approval, do we want that to be by majority or by two-thirds as well?

146
00:11:07,542 --> 00:11:07,942
[SPEAKER_04]: Well,

147
