[SPEAKER_03]: Right.

155
00:11:30,882 --> 00:11:37,386
[SPEAKER_03]: Um, and if we're talking about rare cases, I think we could almost as comfortably make it unanimous.

156
00:11:37,666 --> 00:11:41,128
[SPEAKER_03]: I don't think we want it to be unanimous, but I think two thirds is perfectly reasonable.

157
00:11:42,974 --> 00:11:47,718
[SPEAKER_04]: I think two-thirds for the rejection.

158
00:11:49,740 --> 00:11:53,583
[SPEAKER_04]: For the approval, we can keep it the same.

159
00:11:53,603 --> 00:11:54,724
[SPEAKER_04]: We can keep it the same.

160
