161
00:12:06,675 --> 00:12:07,296
[SPEAKER_04]: Into their position.

162
00:12:12,882 --> 00:12:13,723
[SPEAKER_04]: What do you think to me?

163
00:12:13,904 --> 00:12:15,927
[SPEAKER_03]: I think I think both should be 2 thirds.

