[SPEAKER_04]: I mean, they say more complicated things, but I did find, I think it was Newton that was sort of what, I was trying to find one that described what we had talked about.

182
00:13:50,410 --> 00:13:56,053
[SPEAKER_04]: And I did finally find, it was Newton, I think it was, yeah.

